{"tid":1967550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【動物之森／動物森友會】玩家創AV場景 動物村民變男優推倒女角","createTime":"2020-04-11T04:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T05:18:39.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"79aaf9ed3c97bd0fad51fdca6ed1f0e1c4bf9afb","tid":1967550,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200409/324957794824491008.jpeg/f1eotnwHZ35w2A9EZdShdUPr2Wsq3GuRKFT_TShU_00?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200409%2F324957794824491008.jpeg%2Ff1eotnwHZ35w2A9EZdShdUPr2Wsq3GuRKFT_TShU_00%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=a66910b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200409/324955707373916160.jpeg/nOt4rz3uGQcfA0zjd5MKYzkRoQfBFwOAGwCONRsAjjU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200409%2F324955707373916160.jpeg%2FnOt4rz3uGQcfA0zjd5MKYzkRoQfBFwOAGwCONRsAjjU&h=a87a1bb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200409/324955982050496513.jpeg/tgUagGlVPDlUBcW6UgKfhPqu0s-BUFvr2yIXs9siF7M\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200409%2F324955982050496513.jpeg%2FtgUagGlVPDlUBcW6UgKfhPqu0s-BUFvr2yIXs9siF7M&h=d60dbaf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200409/324956830465921024.jpeg/Q93jg1AoQCsXYxxgofInptoQdJ5wVEcQSlnnw0pZ58M\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200409%2F324956830465921024.jpeg%2FQ93jg1AoQCsXYxxgofInptoQdJ5wVEcQSlnnw0pZ58M&h=2ef835b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n任天堂遊戲《動物森友會》（動物之森／動森）在2019冠狀病毒（COVID-19）肆虐環境下推出，在疫戰下成為神作，而一班出社會工作的成年人多了時間打機，竟令這天真無邪的遊戲多了陣「成人味」。日前，內地遊戲論壇網民分享，有玩家將遊戲玩成「AV拍攝現場」，甚至玩出「未亡人」系列的AV封面，更認真找出樣子有點好色的動物村民，將動森變成人遊戲，令人驚嘆人類想象力的無限。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下載「香港01」App ，即睇城中熱話：<a href=\"https://hk01.app.link/qIZYuEC5LO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk01.app.link%2FqIZYuEC5LO&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479Vebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=d459a57e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk01.app.link/qIZYuEC5LO</a><br />\n<br />\n《動森》是一款全年齡向的遊戲，不單止和色情掛不上邊，連感情線都沒有。不過，日前內地NGA遊戲論壇有網民分享，有神級玩家玩出了18禁遊戲味道，第一張圖片寫上「最終授業」、「最強新人」等字眼，場景是日本AV常見的教室畫面，而該女角色的髮型，網民相信是AV女優波多野結衣，甚至上載了她的照片，指髮型實在太似。<br />\n<br />\n而且玩家裹搬出一班男性的動物角色，巧妙用攝影機遮住女角色的身體，製造裸露感。另一張照片就變成「未亡人」（寡婦）系列，女角色一身黑色和服撐傘造型，右邊用日本寫上「隔壁的狗一直在偷看我，真的很煩」，下圖就變成了拍片現場，動物村民「熊大叔」變成了AV男優在傳統和室內「推倒」女角色，牆上還惡趣味掛上一張已故蘋果教主喬布斯的照片，整個畫片難免令人起奇怪念頭。<br />\n<br />\n圖片在網上引起轟動，相信是玩家開啟了巴獵島的攝影棚功能後，忽發奇想玩出成人效果。雖然未知明確出處，但許多人發現其中一張圖用了簡體字，未有用日本漢字寫法，相信是內地玩家的手筆或是改圖。<br />\n<br />\n有趣的是，男女玩家都會將動森改得成人化，Twitter許多網民都將自己的角色打造得似AV女優，當中穿和服扮成「未亡人」的不在少數，更出現一些「著名場面」，例如一名纖弱女優坐在梳化，身後有一群黑人站着等，看來兒童風的動森還是阻擋不了人類想像力。"},{"pid":"39907583a0cc89e5ac2c6a03987d6baaacf70db2","tid":1967550,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2141f79ba62d945f0387e67d0a4afb4f5c15f79","tid":1967550,"uid":270308,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:35:30.000Z","msg":"意淫仲衰撚過玩國家主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔見支那01屌，不知所謂"},{"pid":"fb55d2862183fb30079203a91619c4dd34d591f0","tid":1967550,"uid":5893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f54f00875ac417f956a04762999f18793ca4afa","tid":1967550,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6237c30218c1b94662bc38dbe1873886083c37b","tid":1967550,"uid":328119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T05:18:39.000Z","msg":"又係哩啲post，返去成人台啦"}]}